quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ndayidde ba Malayika abasimbye ennyiriri ennambulukufu
  37,2,Olwo nno abo abagoba ebire olugoba (bigende bitonnyese enkuba)
  37,3,N'abo abasoma ebigambo ebibuulirira
  37,4,Mazima Katonda wa mmwe ddala ali omu
  37,5,Mukama omulabirizi we ggulu omusanvu n'ensi n'ebyo ebiri wakati wa byombi era Mukama omulabirizi w'ebuvanjuba (n'e bugwanjuba)
  37,6,Mazima ffe twawunda eggulu ly'okunsi n'okulabika obulungi kw'e mmunyeenye (ezirijjudde)
  37,7,N'okulikuuma ku buli Sitane kyewaggula
  37,8,Tezisobola kuwuliriza bitonde ebya waggulu era zikanyugirwa ebitawuliro okuva ku buli luuyi
  37,9,Nga zifuumuulwa emisinde era nga zigenda kufuna ebibonerezo ebitakoma
  37,10,Okugyako (Sitane) eyo enyakula ekigambo kyeba enyakudde olwo nno neekasukirirwa ekitawuliro ekibumbujja
  37,11,"Kale nno babuuze nti bo be bazibu mu kutonda oba ebyo bye twatonda, mazima ffe (bo) twabatonda mu budongo obukwafu"
  37,12,Wabula gwe weewuunya (ng’okungiriza) ate nga bo bajeeja bujeeja
  37,13,Era nga bwe baba babuuliriddwa tebeebuulirira
  37,14,Era bwe balaba akabonero konna (mu bubonero bwa Katonda) nga bajeeja
  37,15,"Era nebagamba nti: kino tekiri okugyako eddogo eryeyolefu"
  37,16,(Nebongerako nti) bwe tuliba tufudde netufuuka ettaka era netuba magumba ameereere abaffe tulizuukizibwa
  37,17,Oba ba kitaffe abaakulembera
  37,18,Gamba nti yee (mulizuukizibwa) nga nammwe mukkakkanyiziddwa
  37,19,Mazima kyo (ekyo kuzuukira) luliba olufuuwa mu ngombe lumu oligenda okulaba nga bo batunula
  37,20,Era baligamba nti zitusanze luno lwe lunaku lw'okusasulwa
  37,21,(Ba Malayika baligamba nti) luno lwe lunaku lw'okwawula (wakati wa balongoofu n’aboonoonyi) olwo lwe mwali mulimbisa
  37,22,(Ba Malayika baliragirwa nti) mukungaanye abo abeeyisa obubi wamu n'ababafaanana n'ebyo bye baasinzanga
  37,23,Nebava ku Katonda olwo nno mubalage ekkubo eridda eri omuliro Jahiimu
  37,24,Era nga (temunnabatwala) mubayimirize (mu bbaliro) mazima bo balina okubuuzibwa
  37,25,"(Olwo nno bagambibwe) nti: mubaddeki lwaki temwetaasa"
  37,26,Wabula bo ku lunaku olwa leero bagenda kukkiriza (nti tebalina bya kukola kuvvuunuka buzibu bwe balibeeramu)
  37,27,Abamu ne boolekera bannaabwe nga bawaanyisiganya ebigambo
  37,28,(Abagoberezi) ne bagamba (bebaagoberera) nti mazima mmwe mwalinga mutujjira nga mutuyita ku ddyo
  37,29,(Abaagobererwa) baligamba nti nedda wabula temwali bakkiriza
  37,30,Era tetwabalinaako buyinza bwonna wabula mwali bantu abeewagguzi
  37,31,Olwo nno ekigambo kya Mukama omulabirizi waffe nekitukakatako (fenna) mazima ddala ffe tuteekwa kukomba (ku bibonerezo)
  37,32,Twababuza era mazima ddala ffe (okugenda okubabuza) twali babuze
  37,33,Mazima bo (ab'emirundi ebiri) bagenda kwegatta mu kibonerezo
  37,34,Mazima ffe bwe tutyo bwe tukola aboonoonyi
  37,35,Mazima bo bwe baagambibwanga nti tewali kisinzibwa kyonna okugyako Katonda baali nga beekuza
  37,36,Nebagamba nti mazima ffe tuyinza okuleka ba katonda baffe ku lw'omuyimbi omulalu
  37,37,Nedda (Nabbi Muhammad talinga bwe bagamba) wabula yajja na mazima era n’akakasa ababaka (abaamukulembera)
  37,38,Mazima ddala mmwe muli ba kukomba ku bibonerezo ebiruma ennyo
  37,39,Era temugenda kusasulwa wabula ebyo bye mwakolanga
  37,40,Okugyako abaddu ba Katonda abalondobemu
  37,41,Abo baliweebwa ebigabirirwa ebimanyiddwa
  37,42,(Biriba) ebibala era nga nebaba nga bo bagabulwa
  37,43,Nga bali mu jjana ez'ebyengera
  37,44,(Baliba) ku bitanda nga buli bamu boolekedde bannaabwe
  37,45,Nga babayisaamu (mu kubagabula) eggiraasi z'ebyo'kunywa eziva mu nsulo ezitakalira
  37,46,(Eby'okunywa ebyo) nga byeru ebiriwoomera abanywi
  37,47,Tebigenda kubaamu kirumya mutwe era nga bwebatagenda kutamiira olw'okubinywa
  37,48,Era baliba balina abakyala ab'amaaso amakkakkamu amanene
  37,49,Abakyala abo balibanga amagi ageegenderezebwa obutayatika
  37,50,Olwo nno abamu neboolekera bannaabwe nga bawaanyisaganya ebigambo
  37,51,Omwogezi (omu) ku bo aligamba nti mazima nze nalina ow'omukwano
  37,52,Yalinga angamba nti abaffe ggwe oli mu abo abakakasa
  37,53,"Nti bwe tulifa netufuuka ettaka n’amagumba ameereere, abaffe tuli baakubalibwa"
  37,54,Omukozi w’obulungi aligamba nti abaffe mulaba ekiri mu muliro
  37,55,Olwo alitunulayo n’amulaba ng’ali mu makkati g’omuliro Jahiimu
  37,56,Aligamba nti ndayidde Katonda wabula kata onzikirize
  37,57,Singa si byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wange nnaalibadde mu baleeteddwa (eri omuliro)
  37,58,Ate ffe tetukyaddayo nakufa
  37,59,Okugyako okufa kwaffe okwasooka era nga tetuli ba kubonerezebwa
  37,60,Mazima ekyo ddala kwo kwe kwesiima okusuffu
  37,61,(N’olwekyo) ku lw’ebintu nga bino abatakabana baalitakabanye
  37,62,Abaffe obwo bwe bugugenyi obulungi oba omuti gwa Zakkuumi
  37,63,Twagussaawo nga kikemo eri abeeyisa obubi
  37,64,Mazima gwo muti guva ku ntobo ya muliro Jahiimu
  37,65,Ebibala byagwo (okumanya bibi) biringa emitwe gya Sitane
  37,66,Mazima bo bagenda kugulyako bagenda kujjuza nagwo embuto
  37,67,Oluvanyuma bagenda kubongeza ku gwo eby'okunywa ebitabuddwa mu lweje
  37,68,Oluvanyuma mazima obuddo bwabwe buli mu muliro Jahiimu
  37,69,Mazima bo baasanga bakadde baabwe nga babuze
  37,70,N’olwekyo bo mu buwufu bwabwe batwalibwa kantindiggwa
  37,71,Era mazima oluberyeberye lwabwe abasinga obungi mu baasooka baabula
  37,72,So nga ate twatuma mu bo abatiisa
  37,73,Kale tunuulira olabe enkomerero y'abaatiisibwa yali etya
  37,74,(Tewali yawona) okugyako abaddu ba Katonda abalondobemu
  37,75,Mazima Nuhu yatukoowoola naffe nno twali abaamwanukula obulungi
  37,76,Netumuwonya n’abantube akabenje akayitirivu
  37,77,Netufuula ezzadde lye nebaba bo nga be basigaddewo
  37,78,Netumulekerawo okwogerwako okulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  37,79,Emirembe gibeere ku Nuhu (n’okwogerwako okulungi) mu bitonde byonna
  37,80,Mazima ffe bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abakozi b’obulungi
  37,81,Mazima (Nuhu) ali mu baddu baffe abakkiriza aba nnamaddala
  37,82,Oluvanyuma twazikiriza abasigadde (abatakkiriza Nuhu)
  37,83,Era mazima ddala Ibrahim ali ku nkolaye(Nuhu)
  37,84,Kubanga yajja ewa Mukama omulabiriziwe n’omutima omuyonjo
  37,85,Bwe yagamba kitaawe n’abantu be nti biki bye musinza
  37,86,Ba katonda abajingirire bemwagala nemuleka Katonda
  37,87,"Olwo Mukama omulabirizi w’ebitonde byonna, ki kye mumulowoozaako"
  37,88,Olwo nno naatunula olutunula mu munyeenye (nga enkola ya bantube bwe yali)
  37,89,(Naagamba nti) mazima nze ndi mulwadde
  37,90,Olwo nebamuvaako nebamulekawo
  37,91,Olwo nadda ku ba katonda baabwe naalyoka abagamba nti lwaki temulya
  37,92,"Mwabaaki, nga temwogera"
  37,93,Olwo kwe kutandika okubatema n’omukono gwe ogwa ddyo
  37,94,Olwo (abantu ba Ibrahim bwe baamanya kyakoze) bajja gyali nga banguwa
  37,95,"(Ibrahim) naagamba nti, musinza ebyo bye mubajja"
  37,96,So nga Katonda yeeyabatonda mmwe n'ebyo bye mukola
  37,97,Nebagamba nti mumuzimbire ekifo (mukikumemu omuliro) olwo nno mumukasuke mu nnabeengeya w’omuliro
  37,98,"Mu kukola ekyo, baagenderera okumukolera olukwe (bamutte) wabula bbo netubafuula ab'awansi (bwe twalemesa olukwe lwabwe)"
  37,99,(Awo Ibrahim naasalawo okusenguka) era naagamba nti mazima nze ngenda ewa Mukama omulabirizi wange ajja kunnungamya
  37,100,Ayi Mukama omulabirizi wange ngabira (omwana) nga wa mu balongoofu
  37,101,Olwo netumusanyusa nti ajja kufuna omwana omulenzi ow'ekisa
  37,102,"Omwana oyo (Ismail) bwe yatandika okutambula naye (Ibrahim) naagamba nti owange mutabani wange nkirabye lunye mu kirooto mazima nze nga nkusala kale tunula olabe, ogamba ki? (Ismail) naagamba nti owange taata kola ekyo kyolagirwa, Katonda nga ayagadde ojja kunsanga nga ndi mu bagumiikiriza"
  37,103,Bombi bwe baamala okwewaayo eri (ekiragiro kya Katonda) naamugalamiza nga amuwunzise
  37,104,Netumukoowoola nti owange Ibrahim
  37,105,"Mazima otuukirizza endooto, mazima ffe bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abalongoosa"
  37,106,Mazima ekyo (ekyatuuka ku Ibrahim n’omwana we) ddala kwe kugezesa okw'olwatu
  37,107,Era (Ismail) twamununula n'ensolo ensuffu eyasalibwa
  37,108,Netumulekerawo okwogerwako okulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  37,109,Emirembe gibeere ku Ibrahim
  37,110,Bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abalongoosa
  37,111,Mazima ye wa mu baddu baffe abakkiriza (abannamaddala)
  37,112,Era twamusanyusa n’okumuwa Ishaak nga nabbi nga wa mu balongoofu
  37,113,Era twamuwa omukisa netuguwa ne Ishaak era mu zadde lyabwe bombi mwalimu omulongoosa n'yeeyisa obubi ow'olwatu
  37,114,Mazima twabunduggula ebyengera ku Musa ne Haruna
  37,115,Netubawonya n’abantu baabwe bombi akabenje ak'amaanyi
  37,116,Netubataasa nebaba bbo nga bawanguzi
  37,117,Bombi twabawa ekitabo ekinnyonnyofu okutangaaza ekkubo
  37,118,Era twabalungamya mu kkubo eggolokofu
  37,119,Era bombi twabalekerawo okwogerwako okulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  37,120,Emirembe gibeere ku Musa ne Haruna
  37,121,Mazima ffe bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abalongoosa
  37,122,Mazima bombi ba mu baddu baffe abakkiriza (abannamaddala)
  37,123,Era mazima ddala Elias wa mu babaka
  37,124,Jjukira ekiseera bwe yagamba abantu be abaffe temutya (Katonda)
  37,125,Musinza ekibumbe ne muleka (Katonda) omutonzi asinga abatonzi bonna
  37,126,Katonda ye Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe era ye Mukama omulabirizi wa bakadde ba mmwe abaasooka
  37,127,Ne bamulimbisa n’olwekyo mazima bo baakuleetebwa (babitebye)
  37,128,Okugyako abaddu ba Katonda abalondemu
  37,129,Era twamulekera okwogerwako obulungi mu balijja oluvanyuma
  37,130,Emirembe gibe ku bantu ba Elias
  37,131,Mazima ffe bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abalongoosa
  37,132,Mazima ye wa mu baddu baffe abakkiriza abannamaddala
  37,133,Era mazima Luutu wa mu babaka
  37,134,(Jjukira) bwe twamuwonya n’abantube bonna
  37,135,Okugyako omukadde (Mukyalawe) eyali mu baasigala
  37,136,Oluvanyuma twazikiriza abaasigala
  37,137,Era mazima mmwe mubayitako (muyita ku matongo gaabwe) ku makya
  37,138,N'ekiro abaffe temutegeera
  37,139,Era mazima Yunus wa mu babaka
  37,140,Jjukira (bwe yasuulawo omulimu Katonda gwe yamukwasa) naalinnya eryato eryali limaze okutikka
  37,141,"(Bwe lyasemberera okusaanawo olw'okuba lyali litisse nnyo), olwo nno (Yunus) yeetaba mu kalulu (ak'okusalawo ab'okukasukibwa mu nnyanja, akalulu kaagenda okuggwa) nga ali mu be kakutte (ne bamukasuka mu nnyanja)"
  37,142,Olwo nno ekyennyanja kwe kumumira nga ye y'anenyezebwa
  37,143,Singa mazima ddala teyali mu batendereza (Katonda)
  37,144,Yandibadde mu lubuto lwakyo okutuusa ku lunaku lwe balizuukizibwa
  37,145,Wabula twamukasuka ku lukalu naye nga yali mulwadde
  37,146,Twamumereza ekimera eky'ekiryo (kimusiikirize kimugobeko n'ensowera)
  37,147,Era twamutuma eri abantu emitwalo kkumi oba okusingawo
  37,148,"Bakkiriza, olwo nno netubeeyagaza okutuuka ebbanga eggere"
  37,149,Kaakano ggwe babuuze (aba Kuraish) nti Mukama omulabiriziwo y'aba n'abawala bo nebaba n’abalenzi
  37,150,Oba abaffe bo baaliwo nga tutonda ba Malayika nga bakazi
  37,151,Abange mazima mu kutemerera kwabwe batuuka n'okugamba nti
  37,152,Katonda yazaala nga ate ddala bo balimba
  37,153,(Katonda) asalawo okutwala abawala n'aleka abalenzi
  37,154,Mwabaaki mulamula mutya (ebintu)
  37,155,Abaffe temwebuulirira
  37,156,Oba mulina obujulizi obweyolefu (nga kye kibakozesa ekyo)
  37,157,Kale muleete ekiwandiiko kyammwe bwe muba ab'amazima
  37,158,"(Abatakkiriza) nebateeka oluganda wakati we (Katonda) n'amajinni, nga ate amajinni gamanyi nti mazima ggo gaakuleetebwa (mu maaso ga Katonda gabitebye)"
  37,159,Katonda musukkulumu ku bye boogera
  37,160,Wabula abaddu ba Katonda abalondobemu (anti bbo tebagwa mu kiti kyabo abamwogerako eby'ensimattu)
  37,161,Kale nno mazima ddala mmwe n'ebyo bye musinza
  37,162,Temusobola mmwe kufiiriza Katonda (ne mumujjako abaddu be)
  37,163,Be ppo oyo y'ewokwesonseka omuliro Jahiimu (oyo musobola okumubuza)
  37,164,(Ba Malayika ne bagamba nti) era tewali n'omu ku ffe okugyako nga alina ekifo ekimanyiddwa
  37,165,Era mazima ffe (bulijjo) ffe tubeera mu nnyiriri (nga tusinza Katonda)
  37,166,Era mazima ffe ddala ffe abatendereza (Katonda)
  37,167,Newaakubadde nga (abakaafiiri) ddala bagamba nti
  37,168,Ddala singa twalina okujjukizibwa nga kuva eri abaasooka
  37,169,Twandibadde abaddu ba Katonda abalondobemu
  37,170,"(Wabula kitalo byonna ebyo bwe byajja nga ne Nabbi Muhammad kwali) baabiwakanya, kale kyaddaaki balimanya"
  37,171,Mazima kyakulembera ekigambo kyaffe eri abaddu baffe abaatumwa
  37,172,Nti mazima bbo ddala be b'okutaasibwa
  37,173,Era mazima eggye lyaffe ddala bo be baba abawanguzi
  37,174,Kale baveeko okutuusa ekiseera ekigere
  37,175,Era batunuulire kyaddaaki baliraba
  37,176,Abaffe ebibonerezo byaffe bye basaba bibatuukeko mangu
  37,177,Lwe birituuka mu lujja lwabwe galiba makya mabi eri abaaweebwa amawulire agabatiisa (omuliro ne batawulira)
  37,178,Era baveeko okutuusa ekiseera ekigere
  37,179,Era tunula kyaddaaki baliraba
  37,180,"Mukama omulabirizi wo, nannyini buyinza musukkulumu Ku ebyo bye boogera"
  37,181,Era emirembe gibeere ku babaka (ba Katonda)
  37,182,Era buli kitendo kya Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde